column5: Saw them on Enid's Blog this morning. Great photos, but they were shot yesterday. NW Ontario is still waiting for Groundhog Day.Thanks Enid.
Looked at that this morning myself, stuck sled and all. Tomahawk webcam has shown vast improvement in the last three days
I really enjoy Enid's blog, and many of the others. Thank you owners for keeping us up to date.
